<h1>About</h1>

<p>
  Keegan Quigley Music is a multi-instrumentalist solo project. Every guitar,
  bass, drum, and vocal track on every release is performed by Keegan.
</p>

<p>
  The songs sit somewhere between garage rock immediacy, stoner rock weight,
  and the kind of personal indie rock songwriting that prioritizes feel over
  polish. Real instruments, played by hand, by one person — a rarity in
  2026's algorithm-shaped music landscape.
</p>

<p>
  The first batch of recordings — <em>Bedroom Demos Vol. 1</em> — was made
  entirely at home, without a studio, in the tradition of artists like Mac
  DeMarco and early Ty Segall. Polished, professionally-mixed versions of the
  strongest tracks follow as Spotify singles. Until then, the home recordings
  live on Bandcamp where they belong.
</p>

